    <title>整洁代码</title>
    <link href="http://treeboy.github.io/2016/02/14/%E6%95%B4%E6%B4%81%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81/"/>
    <id>http://treeboy.github.io/2016/02/14/整洁代码/</id>
